Name: Limousine Parking Simulator
About the game: Have you ever wondered what it's like to park a limousine? Here is about skills and attention. As a personal driver, you will encounter all kinds of obstacles in front of you, which must be avoided nicely and accurately. Your mission as a limousine driver is to learn how to drive almost perfect a limousine. So, be very careful while driving, because you are not driving the cheapest car... You don't have to upset your boss about scratching your car. Good Luck! Game Features : - 3 expensive limousine cars - 10 levels - Daily Spin - Limited time for each level
